{"tid":2434932,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"紐西蘭發生8級地震","createTime":"2021-03-06T00:23:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T03:47:42.000Z","uid":178187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3daee229b5f93c989dca4493d42cb831ebf81394","tid":2434932,"uid":178187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T00:23:33.000Z","msg":"蘋果又用「新」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新西蘭當地時間周五三度發生地震，第三次地震發生在當地時間上午近9時左右，克馬得群島(Kermadec)附近發生強度達8級地震，新西蘭之前已發生兩次地震，這次8級強震促使新西蘭、澳洲及夏威夷發出海嘯警告。民眾都跑上高地暫避，網上影片流傳北島東岸的Tokomaru Bay周五上午有大浪湧至。當局在香港時間8時許指最大規模的海嘯已過，解除海嘯警告。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲傳媒9 NEWS報道首波海嘯湧向北島，引述Tokomaru Bay當地居民指，他見到一道看似是海嘯的巨浪逼近海岸線時都很震驚。比爾德（Chris Beard）說 ：「每個人那一刻都坐在山上，而我們開始熱了，有攝氏32度。」當局呼籲岸邊民眾疏散後，促請他們留在高地上，專家警告海嘯活動會持續幾小時，直至警報除下前，民眾也要認真看待威脅。<br />\n<br />\n新西蘭當地時間周五凌晨2時27分（香港時間周四晚上9時27分）發生首場地震，強度為黎克特制7.1級，震央位於北島東岸城市吉斯伯恩（Gisborne）東北180公里，震源深度10公里。<br />\n<br />\n第二次地震位於克馬得群島附近，強度為7.4級，在當地時間上午6時41分發生，歐洲地中海地震中心（EMSC）指出，這次地震震源深度為10公里。<br />\n<br />\n在發生8級地震後，太平洋海嘯預警中心稱，太平洋地區如瓦努阿圖及法屬新喀里多尼亞（New Caledonia）可能會出現高3米巨浪。中心還說，根據所有可得的數據，預測某些海岸會有破壞性海嘯，較小的海浪最遠可能會傳到日本、俄羅斯、墨西哥和南美海岸。根據美國海嘯預警系統，美屬薩摩亞也發佈了海嘯預警、夏威夷群島發佈了海嘯監察。澳洲也發出海嘯預警。太平洋海嘯預警其後於本港時間周五上午，取消夏威夷的海嘯監察及薩摩亞的預警。<br />\n<br />\n新西蘭基督城2011年2月22日發生黎克特制6.3級地震，造成185人死亡及數以千計民眾受傷。"},{"pid":"30b16fe4528e0797472d385c7850dcd44274b320","tid":2434932,"uid":178187,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T00:25:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AxfSFbq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAxfSFbq.png&h=b39a38ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09a642d7172553112f42f19792cf2d6e1152e263","tid":2434932,"uid":178187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T00:26:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0i8QrRD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0i8QrRD.png&h=a2499a98&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"705a267298ecf923a2bc806000b2a19b861bcd8a","tid":2434932,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T00:26:22.000Z","msg":"又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088dd424880d1e654d7aed496cc2bc1572848353","tid":2434932,"uid":178187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"705a267298ecf923a2bc806000b2a19b861bcd8a","tid":2434932,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T00:26:22.000Z","msg":"又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T00:27:20.000Z","msg":"啱啱好上次311十週年"},{"pid":"bf71d2fa0d31bc3d766787896fd2087c879114bc","tid":2434932,"uid":7824,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T00:27:39.000Z","msg":"震死班藍屍就啱啦"},{"pid":"826b3f5e55baa6e6732955b7ef6d07d7f1ae0cd0","tid":2434932,"uid":178187,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf71d2fa0d31bc3d766787896fd2087c879114bc","tid":2434932,"uid":7824,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T00:27:39.000Z","msg":"震死班藍屍就啱啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T00:28:30.000Z","msg":"藍屍？紐西蘭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a87a373817cc6f85052bb5c788dc216df80a8a53","tid":2434932,"uid":178187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T00:34:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d68da21f630a709e6bb3130deca62f319b826b9","tid":2434932,"uid":178187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T00:38:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"51c3c5b5b040afc503abbd08681a0422d4828518","tid":2434932,"uid":178187,"like":0,"dislik